title: Hearty Chipotle Pork Chili with Quinoa
description: Grab a spoon and dig into tonight's hearty chipotle pork chilli. Lime-infused quinoa, tender peppers and corn round out this bowl of goodness that's warm, filling and perfect for a winters day!

